1. *Majstor* je stigao da popravi mašinu. (*Majstor* - The repairman has arrived to fix the machine.)
2. Molim vas, da li možete pozvati *majstora* za ovaj problem? (Can you please call the *repairman* for this problem?)
3. On je pravi *majstor* u kuhinji. (He is a real *master* in the kitchen.)
4. Ovaj sto je pravi rad *majstora*. (This table is the work of a true *craftsman*.)
5. Da li možete preporučiti dobrog *majstora* za ovu vrstu posla? (Can you recommend a good *specialist* for this type of work?)
6. Moj brat je auto *majstor* i radi u servisu. (My brother is a car *mechanic* and works in a car repair shop.)
7. Videla sam da imaš alatke, da li si *majstor*? (I saw that you have tools, are you a *handyman*?)
8. Kada sam imao problem sa klimom, pozvao sam *majstora* da ga popravi. (When I had a problem with the air conditioner, I called a *technician* to fix it.)
9. *Majstori* su bili na gradilištu čitav dan i uspeli su da završe posao na vreme. (*Workers* were on the construction site all day and managed to finish the job on time.)
10. On je *majstor* u izradi nameštaja od drveta. (He is a *specialist* in making wooden furniture.)